Toughpad API

Packages 
Package Description
com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api
This package provides methods to initialize the Toughpad API library before it is used.
com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.appbtn
Allows control of the customizable buttons on the device, such as the A1, A2, A3, side, and user buttons.
com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.barcode
Provides access to internal and external barcode readers.
com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.magstripe
Provides access to internal and external magnetic stripe readers.
com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.magstripe.magtek
Contains the MagTekMagStripeData class which provides additional information needed to decode magstripes from magtek readers.
com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.serial
Provides access to any connected serial communication devices.
com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.smartcard
Provides access to internal and external smart card readers.
